text:
Cook bounces back, fires Union County over Hawthorne 
Sat, Oct 10, 2015 @ 12:14 am 
UNION COUNTY 36 
HAWTHORNE 18 
Ty Cook bounced back from a rough start with two TD passes, as Union County topped visiting Hawthorne (4-3, 2-1) to maintain control of District 6-1A. ... Darian Robinson scored two first-half TDs for the Fightinâ€™ Tigers (6-0, 2-0). ... Isaiah Johnson also scored on the ground for Union County.
